---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Knowledge Hub">

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow">About the Event</span>
      <h1>Knowledge Hub</h1>
      <p>An annual evening seminar for anyone involved with charities, religious organizations, and not-for-profit organizations.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container content-grid">
      <div class="content-main">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>Each year, the Knowledge Hub brings together experienced professionals who share practical knowledge on topics that matter to the not-for-profit sector. From legal compliance and financial management to governance and risk mitigation, our sessions are designed to equip leaders with actionable insights.</p>

        <h2>Who Attends</h2>
        <p>Board members, treasurers, executive directors, administrators, and volunteers from charities, churches, and not-for-profit organizations across the Greater Toronto Area. Whether you're running a small community group or managing a large charitable organization, the Knowledge Hub has something for you.</p>

        <h2>Format</h2>
        <p>The evening begins with a networking reception, followed by expert-led presentations and Q&amp;A sessions. Light refreshments are provided. A livestream option is available for those unable to attend in person.</p>
      </div>

      <aside class="content-aside">
        <div class="info-block">
          <dl>
            <dt>Next Event</dt>
            <dd>April 23, 2026</dd>
            <dt>Time</dt>
            <dd>5:30 PM – 9:00 PM</dd>
            <dt>Location</dt>
            <dd>The Old Mill, Toronto</dd>
          </dl>
        </div>

        <div class="aside-section">
          <span class="eyebrow" style="color: var(--text-tertiary);">Organized by</span>
          <ul class="org-list">
            <li><a href="#">UCSS Toronto</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">UCPBA</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">UCBA</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="aside-section">
          <span class="eyebrow" style="color: var(--text-tertiary);">With support from</span>
          <ul class="org-list">
            <li><a href="#">Mills &amp; Mills LLP</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    background: var(--surface);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: var(--sp-8) 0;
  }
  .page-hero .eyebrow {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-3);
  }
  .page-hero h1 {
    font-size: 36px;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-3);
  }
  .page-hero p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 560px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 280px;
    gap: var(--sp-8);
    align-items: start;
  }
  .content-main h2 {
    font-size: 22px;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-3);
  }
  .content-main h2:not(:first-child) {
    margin-top: var(--sp-7);
  }
  .content-main p {
    font-size: 15.5px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.65;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .content-aside {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--sp-6);
    position: sticky;
    top: 80px;
  }
  .aside-section {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--sp-2);
  }
  .org-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--sp-1);
    margin-top: var(--sp-1);
  }
  .org-list a {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--navy);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .org-list a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .content-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .content-aside { position: static; }
  }
</style>
